{"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectProtocol"],"kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom","title":"Inherits From"},{"kind":"relationships","type":"conformingTypes","title":"Conforming Types","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10GLibObject15BindingProtocolP","roleHeading":"Protocol","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"symbolKind":"protocol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingProtocol"}],"title":"BindingProtocol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingProtocol"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingprotocol"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/binding_ptr-9m3c1","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/flags","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/source","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/sourceProperty","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/target","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/targetProperty"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Methods","anchor":"Instance-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/bind(property:to:_:flags:transformFrom:transformTo:)","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/dupSource()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/dupTarget()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/get(property:)","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getFlags()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getSource()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getSourceProperty()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getTarget()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getTargetProperty()","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/set(property:value:)","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/unbind()"],"generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingProtocol"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectProtocol","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ObjectProtocol"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Whenever the source property changes, the same value is applied to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"target property; for instance, the following binding:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"c","code":["  g_object_bind_property (object1, \"property-a\",","                          object2, \"property-b\",","                          G_BINDING_DEFAULT);"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"will cause the property named “property-b” of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object2"},{"text":" to be updated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"every time [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.set"},{"type":"text","text":"] or the specific accessor changes the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property “property-a” of "},{"code":"object1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is possible to create a bidirectional binding between two properties","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of two ","type":"text"},{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, so that if either property changes, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"other is updated as well, for instance:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["  g_object_bind_property (object1, \"property-a\",","                          object2, \"property-b\",","                          G_BINDING_BIDIRECTIONAL);"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"c"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"will keep the two properties in sync.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to set a custom transformation function (in both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directions, in case of a bidirectional binding) to apply a custom"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transformation from the source value to the target value before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applying it; for instance, the following binding:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"c","code":["  g_object_bind_property_full (adjustment1, \"value\",","                               adjustment2, \"value\",","                               G_BINDING_BIDIRECTIONAL,","                               celsius_to_fahrenheit,","                               fahrenheit_to_celsius,","                               NULL, NULL);"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"will keep the “value” property of the two adjustments in sync; the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"celsius_to_fahrenheit","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" function will be called whenever the “value”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"property of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"adjustment1"},{"type":"text","text":" changes and will transform the current value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the property before applying it to the “value” property of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"adjustment2"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Vice versa, the "},{"code":"fahrenheit_to_celsius","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" function will be called whenever"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the “value” property of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"adjustment2"},{"type":"text","text":" changes, and will transform the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"current value of the property before applying it to the “value” property","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of "},{"code":"adjustment1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" does not resolve cycles by itself; a cycle like"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["  object1:propertyA -> object2:propertyB","  object2:propertyB -> object3:propertyC","  object3:propertyC -> object1:propertyA"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"might lead to an infinite loop. The loop, in this particular case,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can be avoided if the objects emit the ","type":"text"},{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"notify"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":" signal only if the value has effectively been changed. A binding is implemented using the `GObject`notify"},{"text":" signal, so it is susceptible to all the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"various ways of blocking a signal emission, like [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.signal_stop_emission"},{"text":"]","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.signal_handler_block"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A binding will be severed, and the resources it allocates freed, whenever"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"either one of the "},{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances it refers to are finalized, or when"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding"},{"type":"text","text":" instance loses its last reference."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Bindings for languages with garbage collection can use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"GObject.Binding.unbind","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] to explicitly release a binding between the source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and target properties, instead of relying on the last reference on the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"binding, source, and target instances to drop."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol"},{"text":" protocol exposes the methods and properties of an underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GBinding","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The default implementation of these can be found in the protocol extension below."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For a concrete class that implements these methods and properties, see "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Alternatively, use ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" as a lighweight, "},{"code":"unowned","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reference if you already have an instance you just want to use.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance (or source) and another property on another "},{"code":"GObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance (or target)."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingProtocol/getFlags()":{"title":"getFlags()","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getFlags"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12BindingFlagsV","text":"BindingFlags"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingprotocol\/getflags()","abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves the flags passed when constructing the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Binding","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingProtocol\/getFlags()","type":"topic"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object":{"title":"Object","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The base object type."}],"r